---
description: E2E tests that drive the system as a real user would
alwaysApply: false
---

# E2E tests

- Cover top-N user journeys, not every screen—prioritize revenue / safety paths.
- Stable selectors: `data-testid`, ARIA roles, text content. Never CSS classes that drift.
- Wait on app state (network idle, element visible), not `sleep` / fixed timeouts.
- Clean profile per test; reset auth, cookies, local storage between runs.
- Capture artifacts (screenshot, video, HAR, trace) on failure.
- Treat flakes as bugs: quarantine, root-cause, fix or remove—never retry-until-green.
